metadata.name: Dienach 3906 1/55
metadata.description:
Introducing "Dienach 3906" by Bennett Boundless - an immersive, one-of-a-kind music NFT experience. The NFT takes its inspiration from the incredible story of Paul Amadeus Dienach, a man who lived in the early 20th century, and who claimed to have lived in the distant future. 

Inspired by Dienach's diary, and created to bring this incredible love story to life through music. The song is an immersive journey that takes the listener through the pages of Dienach's diary, painting a vivid picture of the past & future love he described.

As you listen to the track, you'll be transported to a world of otherworldly soundscapes, soaring melodies and deep basslines, evoking the feeling of traveling through time and space.
